      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in showroom-original state, reflecting a standard of preservation rarely encountered in the secondary market. Every surface, from the flawless coachwork to the pristine interior appointments, affirms its distinguished provenance and meticulous maintenance history. This is an acquisition for the discerning collector who demands mechanical and aesthetic perfection without compromise.",
