    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty. It\u2019s been babied since day one and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Not a scratch or a speck on it! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Come take it for a spin!",
