    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a concours-level E46 M3, a pinnacle of atmospheric engineering. This specimen features the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing for a linear power band up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a factory-spec Variable M Differential Lock. The chassis remains structurally flawless with no subframe fatigue, retaining its original suspension geometry and bushings for razor-sharp turn-in. Finished in collector-grade condition with meticulous service records, this is a turn-key investment for the serious driving enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
