    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This 2021 Porsche 718 Cayman is an absolute masterpiece, preserved in what can only be described as showroom-floor condition. From the moment you lay eyes on the Guards Red exterior, the depth of the gloss is staggering, thanks to a professional ceramic coating and full-front paint protection film (PPF) that has kept the nose free of a single stone chip. Every panel gap is laser-straight, and the wheels are entirely devoid of curb rash, wrapped in factory-spec tires with ample tread. Inside, the cabin retains that intoxicating new-car scent. The black leather sport seats show no signs of entry wear or bolster compression, and every piece of switchgear operates with a satisfying, tactile precision. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach; it has been exclusively serviced at authorized Porsche centers with a comprehensive paper trail to prove its pampered life. It has been strictly garage-kept under a breathable cover, never driven in inclement weather, and remains 100% stock. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands perfection, this Cayman offers a like-new driving experience without the wait time of a custom order.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
